至呢度<br />\n<br />\n第十三頁份Log標題係<br />\nMTRC Express Rail Link Contract 802 Mei Lai Road to Hoi Ting Road Tunnel Land Contamination Assessment at Nan Cheong Barging Point<br />\n<br />\n仇思達 先生，我相信你知 MTRC Express Rail Link 係嚟，呢個係高鐵美荔道隧道相關嘅南昌物業地基重置工程，而呢個工程嘅大判，正係中國公司擁有嘅新昌，新昌你唔知乜公司，我之前介紹過，所以我唔排除 仇思達 爛賭，加新昌拖 仇思達 間公司嘅數，條仆街咪賣屎忽做五毛為生。<br />\n<br />\n所以 仇思達 果啲五毛行徑係絕對有得解，而且係涉及龐大嘅金錢利益，講緊找佢啲賭債數有突嘅一條大數目，梗係屎忽有價。<br />\n<br />\n而且 仇思達 間公司，極得共匪信任，點解，睇埋以下文件咪知<br />\n<br />\n高鐵 823a 工程，大江埔至謝屋村隧道，成個工程標題係：Tai Kong Po to Tse Uk Tunnel，拍檔係中國建築喎。你老母，身為本土派，會同中國建築合作嘅咩，死五毛。仲要大江埔至謝屋村中間係乜，菜園村同石崗軍營， 仇思達 唔係高級五毛，點有資格做呢啲咁敏感嘅工程。<br />\n<br />\n仇思達 係乜，冚家鏟，投共冚家鏟，唔駛講，證據明顯，唔到佢唔認。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://martinoei.com/article/26505/仇思達-係乜？有份起高鐵嘅仆街囉\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmartinoei.com%2Farticle%2F26505%2F%E4%BB%87%E6%80%9D%E9%81%94-%E4%BF%82%E4%B9%9C%EF%BC%9F%E6%9C%89%E4%BB%BD%E8%B5%B7%E9%AB%98%E9%90%B5%E5%98%85%E4%BB%86%E8%A1%97%E5%9B%89&d=exB9%2BbP5di4RF4u3Oz7pYqbKco4j3WCMPlNn4btP894%3D&h=d487a606\" target=\"_blank\">https://martinoei.com/article/26505/仇思達-係乜？有份起高鐵嘅仆街囉</a>"},{"pid":"c51851f960675a1b284515f2d7d4708ace92f9fb","tid":1131364,"uid":117679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"140ea08704fb4fd865329c2124c4a07b97ff3c89","tid":1131364,"uid":8762,"like":4,"dislike":28,"score":-24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T16:25:10.000Z","msg":"全香港from day 1 已經知<br />\n大律師公會今日先知？ <br />\n嘩呢班律師真係叻！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n留名等睇律師繼醫生後成為下一個統戰犧牲品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T01:22:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />律師一早統戰咗啦。成個香港律師公會邊個人搞？"},{"pid":"f998948aba0cf0eba38a7068d251da4867851dd5","tid":1131364,"uid":157063,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T01:25:38.000Z","msg":"根本依家個政府都擺明車馬話比你知<br />\n今次修例唔撚關台灣個單野事架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29cf994e59a68ef0960a3861d3b502c5e5277885","tid":1131364,"uid":205733,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T01:26:19.000Z","msg":"「逃犯條例」= 23條加強版<br />\n23條話你顛覆國家，最多係香港拉人香港判刑<br />\n逃犯條例生效，國家話你顛覆國家/尋釁滋事，第二日就消失咗，第三日就抑鬱畏罪自殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"732084fcdf07b80ad4c06a38d9a252a4bf2bed7a","tid":1131364,"uid":85461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T01:32:55.000Z","msg":"憂懷國恨 心暗傷"},{"pid":"e99f20a0821e96bc9dd372a7f622fa91eec3bfa3","tid":1131364,"uid":138233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T01:41:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f5e0c6c11fb55e54181ebbac7fa3e307a9a75d8","tid":1131364,"uid":47558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T01:45:59.000Z","msg":"感謝黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"939fc5b83bbf3feb8231c35358c6b273221c68c1","tid":1131364,"uid":249971,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T01:46:09.000Z","msg":"共產黨食屎啦屌"},{"pid":"60e354240a42c971290dd22673243fe982acc129","tid":1131364,"uid":64710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T02:00:46.000Z","msg":"屌佢老母"},{"pid":"f96fcc12f26a06d8e1baad151551a91bf5971878","tid":1131364,"uid":56926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T02:31:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e